data.meta_description: ANDREAS II OF HUNGARY was born in the year 1176 in Esztergom, Komarom-Esztergom, Hungary, son of BELA III OF HUNGARY and AGNES de CHATILLON. He was married on May 14, 1234 in Székesfehérvár, Fejér, Hungary to Beatrice d'ESTE, they gave birth to 1 child. He was married in the year 1215 in Székesfehérvár, Fejér, Hungary to YOLANDE de COURTENAY, they gave birth to 1 child. He was married in the year 1202 in Esztergom, Komarom-Esztergom, Hungary to GERTRUDE von ANDECHS-MERAN, they had 5 children. He died on September 21, 1235 in Eger, Heves, Hungary. This information is part of Ancestral Trails 2016 by Patti Lee Salter on Genealogy Online.
